---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<Layout title={`Privacy Policy | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
      <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert prose-headings:font-bold prose-a:text-accent prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline pt-32 pb-24 px-6 min-h-screen">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: July 2026</p>

        <p>
          Your privacy is important to me. It is my policy to respect your privacy regarding any information I may collect from you across this website and any other sites I own and operate.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information I Collect</h2>
        <p>
          I only ask for personal information when I truly need it to provide a service to you. I collect it by fair and lawful means, with your knowledge and consent. I also let you know why I’m collecting it and how it will be used.
        </p>
        <p>
          The types of information collected may include your name and email address if you choose to contact me via forms or email. Furthermore, standard connection data such as your IP address and browser type may be logged for basic analytics and security purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
        <p>
          I only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you with your requested service. What data I store, I’ll protect within commercially acceptable means to prevent loss and theft, as well as unauthorized access, disclosure, copying, use or modification.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Third-Party Access</h2>
        <p>
          I don’t share any personally identifying information publicly or with third-parties, except when required to by law. 
        </p>

        <h2>4. External Links</h2>
        <p>
          My website may link to external sites that are not operated by me. Please be aware that I have no control over the content and practices of these sites, and cannot accept responsibility or liability for their respective privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You are free to refuse my request for your personal information, with the understanding that I may be unable to provide you with some of your desired services.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Contact Me</h2>
        <p>
          Your continued use of my website will be regarded as acceptance of my practices around privacy and personal information. If you have any questions about how I handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact me.
        </p>
      </main>
</Layout>
